@startuml
actor "Admin" as A
participant "Frontend" as F
participant "Users API" as API
database "MongoDB" as DB

A -> F: Xem danh sách Khách Hàng (UserList)
F -> API: GET /api/admin/users
API -> DB: Aggregate Users (count Bookings, total Revenue)
DB --> API: userList (with memberType, metrics)
API --> F: 200 OK
F --> A: Hiển thị Bảng User

A -> F: Click "Lịch Sử Đặt" (Drawer)
F -> API: GET /api/admin/users/:id/bookings
API -> DB: find( userId ).populate(services)
DB --> API: userBookings
API --> F: 200 OK
F --> A: Xổ ra Drawer Lịch hẹn
@enduml
